<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy | Asiaa Travel</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

  <!-- Icons -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<!-- Custom CSS -->
<style>
    :root {
        --gold: #ffd400;
        --gold-dark: #ffd400;
        --text: #333;
        --light-bg: #fffdf5;
    }

    body {
        background-image: url("/assets/cubes.png");
        font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Main container spacing */
    .main-wrapper {
        flex: 1;
        padding-top: 40px;
        padding-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .policy-title {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 2.3rem;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .last-updated {
      color: #777;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* Policy Card */
    .policy-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: none;
      padding: 40px 35px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
    }

    /* Section Titles */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gold-dark);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title i {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 1.45rem;
    }

    /* Box at bottom */
    .contact-box {
      background: var(--light-bg);
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: #555;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    /* Responsive adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .policy-card {
        padding: 25px 20px;
      }

      .policy-title {
        font-size: 1.9rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- Header Include -->
  <%- include('./layouts/header') %>

  <div class="container main-wrapper">

    <!-- Title -->
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 2025</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Card -->
    <div class="policy-card mx-auto">

      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title">
          <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill"></i> 1. Who We Are
        </h3>
        <p>Asiaa Travel provides car-booking, taxi, and cab services across Tamil Nadu and South India through our official website.</p>
        <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://asiaa-travel.com" target="_blank">asiaa-travel.com</a></p>
        <p>For privacy-related questions: <strong>support@asiaa-travel.com</strong></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title">
          <i class="bi bi-collection-fill"></i> 2. Information We Collect
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Personal details:</strong> Name, email, phone, pickup/drop locations, travel date/time.</li>
          <li><strong>Booking data:</strong> Itinerary, vehicle type, fare estimate.</li>
          <li><strong>Communication data:</strong> Confirmation messages, support updates.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser details, cookies, usage data.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-gear-fill"></i> 3. Why We Collect Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>To process and manage bookings.</li>
          <li>To send confirmations and travel updates.</li>
          <li>To improve website performance and user experience.</li>
          <li>To prevent fraud or misuse of our platform.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i> 4. Sharing of Information</h3>
        <p>We only share your information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Drivers / service partners required to fulfil your booking.</li>
          <li>Law enforcement when legally required.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>We do NOT sell or rent personal information.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-cookie"></i> 5. Cookies & Tracking</h3>
        <p>Our website may use cookies for performance and analytics. You can disable cookies in browser settings.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 6 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-lock-fill"></i> 6. Data Security</h3>
        <p>We implement reasonable measures to protect your information, but no system is fully secure.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 7 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-folder-fill"></i> 7. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>We retain your data as needed for legal or service-related purposes, then securely delete it.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 8 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-person-check-fill"></i> 8. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 9 -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> 9. Updates to Policy</h3>
        <p>Policy updates will be posted here with a new "Last Updated" date.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 10 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="bi bi-envelope-fill"></i> 10. Contact Information</h3>
        <div class="contact-box">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@asiaa-travel.com</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 9514578005 / 9514878005</p>
          <p><strong>Website:</strong> https://asiaa-travel.com</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('./layouts/footer') %>

</body>

</html>
